H0.text: Blue Gum and Ironbark are species of which genus of Australian tree. Eucalyptus

H1.text: Blue Gum and Ironbark are species of which genus of Australian tree. Acacia

H2.text: Blue Gum and Ironbark are species of which genus of Australian tree. Casuarina

H3.text: Blue Gum and Ironbark are species of which genus of Australian tree. Gum-tree

A4.text: The blue gum E. globulus makes up by far the largest population in the state.

A5.text: In some species (the 'ironbarks' such as E. crebra and E. jensenii) the rough bark is infused with gum resin.
